name: Alex Lee
summary:
Alex Lee is a 29-year-old man who originally hails from San Francisco, California, and currently resides in Los Angeles, California. He is a full stack developer in the software industry and holds a degree from the University of California, Berkeley. With dedication, hard work, and integrity as his core values, Alex is passionate about traveling, hiking, music, and technology. 

He identifies as a straight East Asian man, and his pronouns are he/him/his. Identity-wise, Alex is an atheist and holds liberal political beliefs. He is a Leo as per his zodiac sign and an ENTJ according to the Myers Briggs personality type.

Alex is a non-smoker and drinks occasionally. He is active in terms of exercise and keeps pets - a dog and a reptile. Despite not having children, Alex is open to the idea of having children in the future.

In terms of his ideal partner, Alex is interested in monogamy with a straight woman aged between 24 and 35, who is at least 5'4" and at most 6'1". His potential partner should also desire children in the future, must not smoke, and must exercise at least occasionally. Drinking and use of marijuana or other drugs are deal-breakers for him.
